snippet.title: Andrew Kreisberg @AJKreisberg at 2012 PaleyFest: Fall TV CW Preview Party
snippet.description:
Andrew Kreisberg @AJKreisberg at 2012 PaleyFest: Fall TV CW Preview Party
Toegevoegd door Leslie Harris vorig jaar
Mingle Media TV and Red Carpet Report host, Gabe Lenners, were invited to cover the 2012 PaleyFest: Fall TV Preview Parties celebrating the CW at The Paley Center for Media in Beverly Hills, CA. The program will feature the preview screening of Arrow with an introductory Q&A session with the cast and creative team of the show, followed by free preview screenings of the CW's Arrow, Emily Owens, M.D., and Beauty and the Beast. For more info visit The Paley Center for Media at http://www.paleycenter.org Be sure to visit our Red Carpet Report site for all the details on who won this year including photos and interviews here at http://www.redcarpetreporttv.com. snippet.description:
Interview with Scott Kreisberg
Toegevoegd door actionmarketer 6 jaren geleden
Scott Kreisberg, CEO of One Step Retail Solutions, talks about how to utilize retail point of sale (POS) software technology to maximize profits, and the benefits of selecting a retail technology partner to help retailers increase productivity. Website: http://www.onestepretail.com.
